---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Auto Service in Abule-Egba, Lagos — GAVI AFRICA LIMITED"
  description="Brand-trained service, OEM parts, and 3-year warranty for Toyota and beyond, in Abule-Egba, Lagos. Routine, diagnostics, body & paint, and fleet service."
  activePage="services"
>
<!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span class="crumb-sep">/</span>Services
    </nav>
    <span class="eyebrow">AFTER-SALES SERVICE</span>
    <h1>Service that keeps your car on the road.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Routine work. Deep diagnostics. Panel and paint. Fleet visits. Our techs are brand-trained. Our parts come from Toyota, Bosch, Denso, Aisin, and Advics. Our warranty runs three years on covered repairs.
    </p>
    <div class="page-hero-actions">
      <a href="/#booking" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Service →</a>
      <a href="tel:+2347053009305" class="btn btn-outline">Call +234 705 300 9305</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ STAT STRIP ============ -->
<section class="stat-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div><h4>Brand-trained techs</h4><p>Not generalists. Trained for the brands we service.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L3 7v6c0 5.5 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.5 9-12V7l-9-5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div><h4>3-year warranty</h4><p>100,000 km / 62,137 miles on covered repairs.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div><h4>Early Bird from 6:30 AM</h4><p>Drop your car before work. Out before 8.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 17h2v-5h11v5h2M5 17a2 2 0 104 0M16 17a2 2 0 104 0M16 7h3l2 5M5 7h11v5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div><h4>Mobile workshop</h4><p>We come to your yard. Fleets of 3+ vehicles.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CATEGORY NAV (jump links) ============ -->
<nav class="category-nav" aria-label="Service categories">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="#routine" class="active">Routine</a>
    <a href="#diagnostics">Diagnostics &amp; Repair</a>
    <a href="#body-paint">Body &amp; Paint</a>
    <a href="#specialty">Specialty</a>
    <a href="#fleet">Fleet</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ============ ROUTINE SERVICES ============ -->
<section id="routine" class="svc-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">ROUTINE MAINTENANCE</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Every car has a service rhythm. We follow yours.</h2>
    <p class="section-lede">Five routine intervals from your first 1,000 km to your annual full check. Same parts, same checklist, every visit.</p>

    <div class="svc-grid">

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">FS</span>
        <h3>Free First Service</h3>
        <p>The first service for any brand new vehicle bought from us. Inspection, fluids top-up, and the first checklist run.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">At 1,000 km / 621 miles</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">QS</span>
        <h3>Quick Service</h3>
        <p>Routine drop-off for oil, filters, fluids, and the standard inspection list. Most cars are in and out the same day.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Every 5,000 km / 3,107 miles</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">PMS</span>
        <h3>Periodic Maintenance</h3>
        <p>Scheduled maintenance that catches wear before it turns into a repair. We work to your manufacturer's interval.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Manufacturer interval</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">AMS</span>
        <h3>Annual Maintenance</h3>
        <p>The full once-a-year service. Deeper than QS. We check what the routine intervals don't reach.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Once per year</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">PS</span>
        <h3>Preventive Service</h3>
        <p>Pre-trip, pre-rainy-season, pre-handover. We run the inspection list before you need to know something works.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">By appointment</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ DIAGNOSTICS & REPAIR ============ -->
<section id="diagnostics" class="svc-section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">DIAGNOSTICS &amp; REPAIR</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Strange noise. Warning light. Hard start. We find it, then we fix it.</h2>
    <p class="section-lede">Computer diagnostics, targeted repair, warranty work, and after-market install. Every job ends with a quality check.</p>

    <div class="svc-grid">

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">DS</span>
        <h3>Diagnostic Service</h3>
        <p>Computer scan and full-system check. We tell you what's wrong and what it costs to fix, before any work starts.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Same-day quote</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">RR</span>
        <h3>Running Repair</h3>
        <p>Targeted fix for a specific fault. Brake squeal, AC out, alternator down. We replace what failed, with OEM parts.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">OEM parts</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">WR</span>
        <h3>Warranty Repair</h3>
        <p>Covered repairs on brand new vehicles bought from us. Three years or 100,000 km, whichever comes first.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">3 yr / 100,000 km</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">AM</span>
        <h3>After-Market Installation</h3>
        <p>Android units, reverse cameras, parking sensors, sound systems. Clean install. No loose wires.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Walk-in or booked</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">ERS</span>
        <h3>Emergency Recovery</h3>
        <p>You break down, we come and pick the car up. Work-hours only for now; full 24/7 coming once the truck fleet expands.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Mon-Sat work hours</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">SP</span>
        <h3>Spare Parts</h3>
        <p>Need a part to keep working on your car yourself? We supply Toyota, Bosch, Denso, Aisin, Advics, and more.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Walk-in counter</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ BODY & PAINT (featured) ============ -->
<section id="body-paint" class="svc-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-svc">
      <div class="feature-svc-visual">
        <img src="/images/body-paint.jpg" alt="Spray gun refinishing a car panel" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <span class="svc-code" style="background:var(--gavi-blue-tint);color:var(--gavi-blue);font-weight:900;font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:0.08em;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:var(--s-4);">BPR</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Body &amp; Paint Repair.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:17px;color:var(--ink-mute);line-height:1.6;">
          Bumper scrape, panel dent, full repaint. We match colour to the original code and finish to show-room standard. Booth-cured. Polished. Inspected.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Colour-matched paint to the original code</li>
          <li>Booth-cured for finish quality</li>
          <li>Panel beat, weld, and replacement</li>
          <li>Insurance assessment cooperation</li>
          <li>Quality inspection before handover</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/#booking" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Body &amp; Paint Job →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ SPECIALTY SERVICES (dark) ============ -->
<section id="specialty" class="svc-section dark">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow on-dark">SPECIALTY DROP-OFF</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Built around your schedule.</h2>
    <p class="section-lede">Lagos traffic is what it is. You shouldn't lose a working day to a service. These options fix that.</p>

    <div class="svc-grid">

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">EBS</span>
        <h3>Early Bird Service</h3>
        <p>Drop your vehicle from 6:30 AM, on your way to work. We start the job before 8.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">From 6:30 AM · T&amp;Cs apply</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">ONS</span>
        <h3>Overnight Service</h3>
        <p>Drop after work, collect the next morning. Best for diagnostics that need a long settle.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Drop-off PM, collect AM</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">WES</span>
        <h3>Weekend Service</h3>
        <p>Saturday service for people who can't take time off work. Same techs, same checklist.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Saturdays 8 AM - 2 PM</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">MWS</span>
        <h3>Mobile Workshop</h3>
        <p>Our service van drives to your yard, office, or compound. We service your fleet on site.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Min. 3 vehicles · T&amp;Cs apply</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">GSW</span>
        <h3>GAVI Service on Wheels</h3>
        <p>The single-vehicle mobile service. Same kit, on your street. Launching once the second van lands.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Launching soon</div>
      </div>

      <div class="svc-card">
        <span class="svc-code">ERS</span>
        <h3>Emergency Recovery</h3>
        <p>Broken down on the road? Call us. We come and tow during work hours; 24/7 once the truck fleet grows.</p>
        <div class="svc-detail">Work hours for now</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FLEET CALLOUT ============ -->
<section id="fleet" class="fleet-callout">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fleet-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow on-dark" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">FLEET &amp; CORPORATE</span>
        <h2>One contract. Every vehicle on your payroll.</h2>
        <p>From insurance brokers to schools to faith organisations, we run scheduled service for fleets of 3 to 300. Periodic checks, repair, mobile-workshop visits to your yard, and one consolidated bill at month-end.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-on-light">Talk to our fleet desk →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="fleet-stats">
        <div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-num">10+</div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-label">Active corporate clients</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-num">3+</div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-label">Vehicles minimum</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-num">24h</div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-label">Turnaround on routine</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-num">1</div>
          <div class="fleet-stat-label">Service desk contact</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ BOTTOM CTA ============ -->
<section class="booking-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="booking-cta-card">
      <span class="eyebrow">READY TO BOOK</span>
      <h2>Tell us what's wrong. We'll handle the rest.</h2>
      <p>Fill the form on our home page and we'll call you back within the hour during work time. Or speak to a Service Advisor now.</p>
      <div class="booking-cta-actions">
        <a href="/#booking" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Service →</a>
        <a href="tel:+2347053009305" class="btn btn-outline">Call +234 705 300 9305</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/2348079000009" class="btn btn-outline">WhatsApp us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>

<style>
/* Services page specific */
  .stat-strip { background: var(--paper-soft); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding: var(--s-8) 0; }
  .stat-grid { display: grid; gap: var(--s-6); grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  @media (min-width: 540px)  { .stat-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .stat-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); } }
  .stat { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--s-3); }
  .stat-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 36px; height: 40px; background: var(--gavi-blue);
    color: #fff;
    -webkit-clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0 75%, 0 25%);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0 75%, 0 25%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .stat-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
  .stat h4 { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .stat p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-mute); line-height: 1.4; }

  /* Category nav (sticky jump links) */
  .category-nav {
    background: var(--paper); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 40;
  }
  @media (min-width: 880px) { .category-nav { top: 71px; } }
  .category-nav .container {
    display: flex; gap: var(--s-2);
    padding-top: var(--s-3); padding-bottom: var(--s-3);
    overflow-x: auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .category-nav a {
    flex-shrink: 0; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink-soft);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line); transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .category-nav a:hover, .category-nav a.active {
    background: var(--gavi-blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--gavi-blue);
  }

  /* Service category section */
  .svc-section { padding: var(--s-16) 0; }
  .svc-section.alt { background: var(--paper-soft); }
  .svc-section.dark {
    background: var(--ink); color: #D8E0EC;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .svc-section.dark h2, .svc-section.dark h3, .svc-section.dark h4 { color: #fff; }
  .svc-section.dark .section-lede { color: #B8C5D6; }
  .svc-section.dark::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -10%; right: -5%;
    width: 40%; height: 60%;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 60 70'><polygon points='30,0 60,17.5 60,52.5 30,70 0,52.5 0,17.5' fill='none' stroke='%235B96D0' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.5'/></svg>");
    background-size: 80px 92px; opacity: 0.18; pointer-events: none;
  }
  .svc-section.dark > .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .svc-grid {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-5);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  @media (min-width: 540px)  { .svc-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .svc-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }

  .svc-card {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: var(--s-6);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s-3);
  }
  .svc-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--gavi-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.06);
  }
  .svc-card .svc-code {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--gavi-blue-tint); color: var(--gavi-blue);
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .svc-card h3 { font-size: 18px; }
  .svc-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-mute); line-height: 1.5; flex-grow: 1; }
  .svc-card .svc-detail {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-weight: 600;
    padding-top: var(--s-3); border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .svc-section.dark .svc-card {
    background: var(--ink-soft); border-color: #2A3A52; color: #D8E0EC;
  }
  .svc-section.dark .svc-card:hover { border-color: var(--gavi-blue); }
  .svc-section.dark .svc-card .svc-code {
    background: var(--gavi-blue); color: #fff;
  }
  .svc-section.dark .svc-card p { color: #B8C5D6; }
  .svc-section.dark .svc-card .svc-detail { color: #fff; border-color: #2A3A52; }

  /* Featured service (body & paint) */
  .feature-svc {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-8); align-items: center;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .feature-svc { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: var(--s-12); } }
  .feature-svc-visual {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.12);
    position: relative;
  }
  .feature-svc-visual svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .feature-list { list-style: none; margin: var(--s-5) 0 var(--s-6); }
  .feature-list li {
    padding: var(--s-2) 0; padding-left: var(--s-6);
    position: relative; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 12px;
    width: 18px; height: 18px; background: var(--gavi-blue); color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Fleet callout */
  .fleet-callout {
    background: var(--gavi-blue);
    color: #fff; padding: var(--s-12) 0;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fleet-callout::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -20%; left: -10%;
    width: 50%; height: 150%;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 60 70'><polygon points='30,0 60,17.5 60,52.5 30,70 0,52.5 0,17.5' fill='none' stroke='%23FFFFFF' stroke-width='1' opacity='0.4'/></svg>");
    background-size: 80px 92px; opacity: 0.15; pointer-events: none;
  }
  .fleet-callout > .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .fleet-grid {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-8); align-items: center;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  @media (min-width: 880px) { .fleet-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: var(--s-12); } }
  .fleet-callout h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .fleet-callout h2 { font-size: 40px; } }
  .fleet-callout p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 16px; max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: var(--s-6); }
  .fleet-callout .btn-on-light { background: #fff; color: var(--gavi-blue); }
  .fleet-callout .btn-on-light:hover { background: var(--gavi-blue-tint); }
  .fleet-stats {
    display: grid; gap: var(--s-5); grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); padding-left: var(--s-6);
  }
  .fleet-stat-num { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .fleet-stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* Bottom CTA section */
  .booking-cta { background: var(--paper-soft); }
  .booking-cta-card {
    background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: var(--s-10);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 26, 43, 0.06);
  }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .booking-cta-card { padding: var(--s-16) var(--s-10); } }
  .booking-cta-card h2 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) { .booking-cta-card h2 { font-size: 40px; } }
  .booking-cta-card p {
    font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-mute);
    max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);
  }
  .booking-cta-actions {
    display: flex; gap: var(--s-3); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
